ec45285c456d        python-docker         "python3 -m flask ru…"   28 minutes ago      Exited (0) 20 minutes ago                       agitated_moser
fb7a41809e5d        python-docker         "python3 -m flask ru…"   37 minutes ago      Exited (0) 36 minutes ago                       goofy_khayyam
```
